    "about": "{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"6s8u1\",\"text\":\"Having spent years immersed in the world of F1 data, we noticed that many organizations were using the same outdated methods for extracting, processing, and augmenting their data. It became clear that a more flexible and standardized approach to storing, managing, querying, and retrieving data was necessary to enable better insights and unlock the full potential of their data.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"cktmq\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"d401l\",\"text\":\"To address this need, we created The Regno Standard and The Regno Toolbox - a cloud-based data platform that provides a comprehensive and adaptable framework for managing data. Our solution ensures that you can capitalize on all the insights your data has to offer, with the ability to easily store, manage, and query your data in a secure and scalable environment. With our tools, you'll have the power to gain valuable insights into your data and make informed decisions to drive your business forward.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}",
