    "about": "{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"ahlsl\",\"text\":\"Our Purpose:\\t     Eliminate waste in the freight industry.\\t\\t\\t\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[{\"offset\":0,\"length\":58,\"style\":\"BOLD\"}],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"59hp0\",\"text\":\"Our Mission:\\t\\t      To enable any business, to ship to any \\n                                       product, to any customer, anywhere in the \\n                                       world. (Big Data is critical to our strategy)\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[{\"offset\":0,\"length\":226,\"style\":\"BOLD\"}],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"93o7t\",\"text\":\"Digital Freight\\t\\t We utilised our digital experience and \\n                                        repositioned www.p4d.co.uk as a digital \\n                                        freight forwarder in February 22, creating \\n                                        an open API for channel partners.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"8mtec\",\"text\":\"We have two revenue streams: \",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[{\"offset\":0,\"length\":29,\"style\":\"BOLD\"},{\"offset\":0,\"length\":29,\"style\":\"UNDERLINE\"}],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"cg9ar\",\"text\":\"(1) direct business customers from p4d.co.uk and \",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"cu9h0\",\"text\":\"(2) channel partner revenues from API connections.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"38iqi\",\"text\":\"Direct Customers\\t\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[{\"offset\":0,\"length\":17,\"style\":\"BOLD\"},{\"offset\":0,\"length\":17,\"style\":\"UNDERLINE\"}],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"jf3n\",\"text\":\"P4D is typically ranked 1-3 on Google UK for key freight terms including ‚ÄúSea Freight China‚Äù, ‚ÄúAir Freight USA‚Äù, ¬†‚ÄúSea Freight USA‚Äù + many more. \",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"g7p3\",\"text\":\"This Google presence has delivered 15,974 business website visits, from 148 industries over the last 9 months. (This is only from static IP addresses.)\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"cm2j0\",\"text\":\"Those 16k business visitors have a combined t/o of ¬£489bn and an estimated annual freight spend of ¬£30bn. They represent just 12% of our traffic.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"avaq6\",\"text\":\"The technology typically quotes 115,000 freight movements per month.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"cn9p7\",\"text\":\"We are at the early stages of monetising these visitors and acquired 1,922 new business customers in Q1 2023. Current annual run rate turnover is ¬£5m and -¬£0.3m EBITDA.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"eau9e\",\"text\":\"Channel Partnerships\\t\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[{\"offset\":0,\"length\":20,\"style\":\"BOLD\"},{\"offset\":0,\"length\":20,\"style\":\"UNDERLINE\"}],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"d81be\",\"text\":\"We have 3 live ‚Äúchannel partnerships‚Äù where third party freight platforms consume our digital services and book a percentage of their quotes with us.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"6atcd\",\"text\":\"We have 1 live ‚Äúchannel partnership‚Äù where our rates and services are embedded into another parties software to provide a shipping solution.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"6ll31\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"ea6pg\",\"text\":\"In May 22 the technology quoted ¬£2.3m of freight movements and in May 23 it quoted ¬£65.4m.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"eq93\",\"text\":\"So the annualised increase is from ¬£28m RR to ¬£784m RR of freight quotes between May 2022 & May 2023 and we expect this number to exceed ¬£1bn within 9 weeks.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"7jmgi\",\"text\":\"We have 46 target channel partnerships with an audience of 181m global business customers.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"1o1ga\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}",
