    "about": "{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"4affs\",\"text\":\"Navigating the vast seas of the maritime industry, Shipergy stands as a beacon of innovation and efficiency. Founded with the mission to revolutionize the $120 billion fuel trading market, we seamlessly blend traditional bunker trading with state-of-the-art SaaS solutions, steering the industry towards a future of transparency and sustainable growth.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"b28u3\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"efpqe\",\"text\":\"In an era where the shipping industry is plagued by opaque fuel pricing, uncertain wait times, and unpredictable fuel quality, Shipergy emerges as a solution to these pressing challenges. Our advanced software products, utilized by an expanding network of 30 companies, provide real-time insights into fuel quality, availability, and pricing, enabling informed and timely decision-making.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"dk039\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"46ev6\",\"text\":\"Beyond software, Shipergy's robust marine fuel trading business is a testament to our impact, already generating a monthly gross profit of $100,000. As the industry embarks on the essential journey towards digitization and decarbonization, Shipergy leads the charge, offering unrivaled expertise and innovative solutions to propel the maritime sector into a new age of efficiency and environmental responsibility.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}",
