    "achievements": "{\"blocks\":[{\"key\":\"iv1m\",\"text\":\"Ocushield is operating a strong omni channel business ¬£2.5m run rate revenue biz, meaning revenue is diversified across website (45%), amazon (40%) and B2B (15%)\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"4v9g0\",\"text\":\"Successful product development and launch of eye supplements, eye masks and an online eye screening service in the last 12 months (with less than ¬£2k marketing spend and in excess of ¬£110k sales for physical products). Our strategy has moved from a blue light blocker brand to an integrated eye health business, something no one is doing. \",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"8cf6n\",\"text\":\"Ocushield is perfectly positioned to win ‚Äì this is the existing sales (including USA growth), team (embedded in eye care), brand and a visual tool that has been exceptionally well received since its launch 2 months ago\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"490pd\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"ckkvn\",\"text\":\"What we are excited about:\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"3fkps\",\"text\":\"With ¬£150k ARR worth of future contracts secured for our eye screening service (Patient Navigator, PirkX) we are focussed on our Ocushield eye screener generating significant uplift in revenue but also customers for our physical products\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"c8753\",\"text\":\"Designed so the eye screening service acts as a marketing channel through product recommendations on the results page and via opted in emails allowing us to communicate with users. Negotiation stage pipeline includes employers such as AON, Britvic, FIS Global and insurers such as Lloyds Online Pharmacy, Benenden Health and Vitality.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"6kvef\",\"text\":\"Our brand has numerous retail partnerships secured, such as WHSmith Travel (August 2023) and QVC USA (August 23) to add to the revenue that partners like John Lewis (¬£110k per annum) generate as well as winning a King's Award for international trade as 40% of trade is from USA\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"7iq8h\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"feg87\",\"text\":\"Ask\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"65g6h\",\"text\":\"We are raising a ¬£250k seed extension (¬£65k committed) round to accelerate sales of the Ocushield eye screener service. We are also building the team to ensure scalability for Series A. Our goal is to protect 10m eyes by 2025.\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"55lep\",\"text\":\"\",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}},{\"key\":\"9am88\",\"text\":\" \",\"type\":\"unstyled\",\"depth\":0,\"inlineStyleRanges\":[],\"entityRanges\":[],\"data\":{}}],\"entityMap\":{}}",
